 />\nA large number of protestors were arrested on 29/9. 96 people, several of them being HKU students, are charged with riots. Their cases will be mentioned at West Kowloon Magistrates&rsquo; Courts on 2/10. HKUSU urges schoolmates to show their support at the venue. The details are as follows -<br />\n<br />\nDate: 2 October 2019<br />\nTime: 9:00 a.m.<br />\nVenue: Court No.1, 4/F, West Kowloon Magistrates&rsquo; Courts<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">義士唔係CONDOM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:59:51.000Z","msg":"九點啦"},{"pid":"6b3a5706c5794ea5db06fe12682c92e634422799","tid":1610953,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:01:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4359ea100799a46f39d9ef518afeea24c5ec1b05","tid":1610953,"uid":314560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:07:11.000Z","msg":"本身返緊學 宜家係東隧諗緊點去"},{"pid":"88de9af627e5e3460e95e2d0a428ae45ca52127f","tid":1610953,"uid":183675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:12:41.000Z","msg":"遲到係咪入得 而家仲有無位"},{"pid":"a55ec7d4ceb061bd156353c60f9c8c16db8f3fe0","tid":1610953,"uid":97948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:16:06.000Z","msg":"搭的士去 好塞車 到而家都未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2516ff13c27ba38e23b201878ff2897192f835ab","tid":1610953,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:22:07.000Z","msg":"地下大堂有幾百人企緊"},{"pid":"8957e92f157ed144a9705671025854ebc62f18e0","tid":1610953,"uid":169819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:24:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56fabfb500c26a0cd85e71b42d5bd6ed1c7837e6","tid":1610953,"uid":25562